{"tid":1657004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今《施政報告》或會重提「明日大嶼」計劃","createTime":"2019-10-16T01:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T02:01:27.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c1dab5be2d853bfa3bd5cb1311039d6816969458","tid":1657004,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"傳將引條例 收農地棕地建公營屋<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n　　此外，有消息指，施政報告將宣布政府引用《收回土地條例》收回農地、棕地及寮屋地，百分百比例興建公屋、首置盤等，包括目標在未來5年收回逾700公頃新界農地及棕地，土地共享先導計劃亦會在今年公布，包括成立新獨立委員會考慮申請，且會重提「明日大嶼」計劃；房委會將研究加快出售餘下4萬伙租置屋邨單位。鄉議局主席劉業強認為在現有機制下，土地持有人無議價能力，如政府收回農地建屋，不應再以農地價值計算地價。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n　　其他民生措施方面，消息稱將為全民交通補貼加碼，由現時超出400元車費即補貼25％，增至30％水平；領取綜援學生發放2,500元津貼恒常化；深圳灣口岸改為24小時通關等。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/internationalaffairs/news/62506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Flifestyle%2Finternationalaffairs%2Fnews%2F62506&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVnWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=5ccd4124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/internationalaffairs/news/62506</a>"},{"pid":"7d092ba4e46b96353beea57a01467a617d9427a2","tid":1657004,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"541264596a2327cef845d73d5b051c442c84512b","tid":1657004,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bf6dbbd4d59c1bcad734c2f605a6eb5685b49f","tid":1657004,"uid":82640,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"怪唔得今日地鐵繼續早收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5610fc70c5b3a5d992a2c889992e2c88d133175","tid":1657004,"uid":82125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,